name: Learn UI/UX Design For Begginers
desc: In this course By learning UX design, you can become a more valuable asset to your current employer or you can change your whole career and reach out to potential employers (yourself included). And, who knows, once you have got a taste of UX, you might dive into UI design and keep expanding your knowledge and skill set.
details: Visual Elements of User Interface Design
UX Design Fundamentals
Web Design: Strategy and Information Architecture
Web Design: Wireframes to Prototypes
